Package: spNetwork
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Analysis on network
Version: 0.1.1.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jeremy", "Gelb", email = "jeremy.gelb@ucs.inrs.ca",role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Philippe", "Apparicio", email="philippe.apparicio@ucs.inrs.ca", role=c("ctb")))
Description: The spNetwork packages provides functions to perform spatial analysis on network.
    In its actual form, it allows to calculate Network Kernel Density Estimate, and to build
    spatial matrices (listw object spdep like) to calculate indicators like Moran I with network
    constraint neighbourhood.
